        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>The AC condenser tubes may be subject to fatigue in HPV Models due to excessive hose movement at
                    the condenser fittings. It has been determined that the plastic clip supporting the tubes to and
                    from the condenser mat not be adequate for all applications.
                </para>
                <para>A production change has been implemented, see Table 1 for In-Effect Dates, to replace the plastic
                    clip with two rubber coated cushion clamps (P-clips).
                </para>
